70650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T11:09:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你仆街了，我個時攪左2年先殺得晒。一公一乸，一個月會生2000隻出黎的，繁殖得好快！</blockquote><br />\n點殺呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b71118f2b80d74803fad400c8e9436773e9b344f","tid":297641,"uid":11779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T11:40:27.000Z","msg":"更新 我已經戰勝木蚤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}